title: 248: The Return of Zeke
itunes:title: 248: The Return of Zeke
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks preview the pivotal Seahawks vs. Cowboys matchup (00:53) before diving into the rest of the week 16 NFL slate (5:48). The guys also pick players that need to step up (19:43) and debate if the Rams or the Jags have a better shot at reaching the Super Bowl (22:45).
